      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. This unit delivers a visceral 8,250 RPM redline with crisp response from its individual throttle bodies. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring neutral handling and excellent power-down on corner exit. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including addressed rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly is protected. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the suspension kinematics and powertrain synchronization remain tight, offering a pure analog driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
